      <title>众议院共和党议员敦促指定 TikTok 外国代理人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/tiktok-foreign-agent-designation-pressed-by-key-house-republican</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位众议院共和党高层威胁要传唤司法部，以确定该机构是否正在调查 TikTok 是否违反了要求外国势力代理人向政府登记的美国法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/tiktok-foreign-agent-designation-pressed-by-key-house-republican</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩科瑞以巨额利润进一步推动商品贸易繁荣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/mercuria-earns-2-7-billion-in-second-best-year-for-profits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩科瑞能源集团有限公司 (Mercuria Energy Group Ltd.) 迎来了有史以来第二好的盈利年份，尽管 2023 年价格波动性有所下降，但该公司与其他主要大宗商品交易公司一样从能源市场获得了巨额横财。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/mercuria-earns-2-7-billion-in-second-best-year-for-profits</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 12:40:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Uber 支持的电动自行车初创公司 Lime 规划车队扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/uber-backed-e-bike-startup-lime-planning-global-fleet-expansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Lime 是 Uber Technologies Inc. 支持的共享电动自行车和踏板车网络运营商，计划今年投资超过 5500 万美元来扩大其全球车队。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-07/uber-backed-e-bike-startup-lime-planning-global-fleet-expansion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
